{"tid":1867541,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"各位醫護，可唔可以罷落去？","createTime":"2020-02-07T08:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T09:13:59.000Z","uid":223428,"like":24,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e1cc995a0450873e3bfde9dc6b4bbffb7e1920","tid":1867541,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:12:19.000Z","msg":"對唔住，我係一個冇工罷的學生，多謝你們曾經醫過我，不過可不可以罷落去呀？<br />\n<br />\n因為呢，你們唔夠裝去醫病，根本保護唔到自己，你都病左，你點醫人呢？隨時連累你的同事呀。關唔封的話，你們本來已經不夠的人手還要應付更多的病人，根本幫唔到人架。<br />\n<br />\n可摸耳唔好比香港有更多的謝婉雯的故事呢？可摸耳去工會投下罷工的一票呢？時間無多，呢個唔係政治問題，係人命呀！事情比Poly U更嚴峻，波及的是每一個市民的生命，不分藍黃。<br />\n<br />\n求下你們繼續罷下去啦&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"962ab35fb04805b6cfd3a06c5f714264df8419db","tid":1867541,"uid":285371,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:12:33.000Z","msg":"「我本人僅此聲明，就算社區爆發，依然支持醫護繼續罷工，直至政府落實封關及其它訴求！」<br />\n<br />\n只要所有公民社會嘅個體都咁做，HAEA嘅人睇到，或者會回心轉意，堅持罷工到底"},{"pid":"a8d914b6c1f4cccd0ede312a5c68268fe928dfc7","tid":1867541,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:12:36.000Z","msg":"推 支持醫護"},{"pid":"75fb46f0a62633f4d44b6705238bbd011c34b5b1","tid":1867541,"uid":268519,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68AR9A8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68AR9A8.jpg&h=dbe3ec9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【延長罷工計劃投票】<br />\n投票截至今日下午四時半<br />\n只限會員</span></span></strong><br />\n￼<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf_VSITn5RwMPGSP36LWB06DYnns4wnLlsHi2-PBumry03GHw/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSf_VSITn5RwMPGSP36LWB06DYnns4wnLlsHi2-PBumry03GHw%2Fviewform&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=fed72aab\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf_VSITn5RwMPGSP36LWB06DYnns4wnLlsHi2-PBumr